description: aggregated usage data for an account.

nested_items.name: timeRange
nested_items.description: The inclusive time period that the usage data applies to. Possible values are: MONTH_TO_DATE, for the current calendar month to date; and, PAST_30_DAYS, for the preceding 30 days.

nested_items.name: usageTotals
nested_items.description: An array of objects that contains the results of the query. Each object contains the data for a specific usage metric.

nested_items.name: currency
nested_items.description: The type of currency that the value for the metric (estimatedCost) is reported in.

nested_items.name: estimatedCost
nested_items.description: The estimated value for the metric.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The name of the metric. Possible values are: AUTOMATED_OBJECT_MONITORING, to monitor S3 objects for automated sensitive data discovery; AUTOMATED_SENSITIVE_DATA_DISCOVERY, to analyze S3 objects for automated sensitive data discovery; DATA_INVENTORY_EVALUATION, to monitor S3 buckets; and, SENSITIVE_DATA_DISCOVERY, to run classification jobs.
